Officer Sales Planning & Operations‎
Mobilink GSM (PMCL)
-
Lahore
The ideal candidate should:
Hold at least a Bachelor’s degree in Business/IT.
Have 1-2 years’ work experience in the relevant field.
Job Description:
Perform and handle projects, initiatives & deliverables as assigned from time to time by line manager.
Analyze and report the performance of sales team on daily, weekly, monthly basis.
Calculate the incentive/commission of ES team as per their performance.
Manage HR related issues of outsourced ES staff nationwide.
Coordinate and follow up with other teams (internal/external) regarding essential day to day activities.
Essential Skills
Proficiency in operating MS Office Suite, specifically MS Excel
Knowledge of database, programming, web development
Sales planning techniques and skills
Strong written and verbal communication skills
Desirable Skills
Strong analytical and decision making skills
Good leadership skills
Customers (Target Market)
Channel Sales
